
The nosetests tool is required to run the test scripts. The document provides
an overview of the installation of nosetests.

(Install all: pip install -r ./requirements.txt)


1. Install Python 3
===================

$ sudo apt install python3-pip
$ sudo apt install python-pip


2. Install websockets and opcua
===============================

$ sudo pip install websocket
$ sudo pip install websocket-client
$ sudo pip install opcua


3. Install nosetests
====================

$ sudo pip install distribute
$ sudo pip install nose
$ sudo pip install virtualenv


4. Execute tests
================

Change to directory <Project-Directory>/ftest an run test script

$ sh test.sh

